Text.Value: |My dosage was a bit too generous it seems. No matter, I'd rather it sting a bit than you die to an assassin's poison of choice. Now, I am yours, if you'd like another.|
I am yours. Come to me.
I have never needed anyone. But I want you.
What a wonderful distraction you are.
I could lose myself in you.
Enough. We still have a war to fight.
|Not now but maybe later, when you've sorted the doses better.|
